    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232355>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Male genitalia. Melibrueelia novaeseelandiae: (A) holotype; (B, C) two paratypes. Brueelia callaeincola: (D) holotype. Scale bars = 0.05 mm." ;
